videoDetails.title: Halloween Infrastructure Update - 27th October 2023

Spooky selection of updates!

 Looking for content on a particular topic? Search the channel. If I have something it will be there!

03:53 - Cosmos DB MongoDB Synapse Link

04:17 - PostgreSQL Flexible auto-grow
05:10 - SQL 2014 ESU
05:24 - Email sender change
05:48 - ASR built-in Azure Monitor alerts
06:19 - Close
